<span class="honorific-suffix" style="font-size: small"><small style="font-size:85%;"><a href="/wiki/List_of_Imams" title="List of Imams" class="mw-redirect">12th</a> <a href="/wiki/Imamah_(Shia_doctrine)" title="Imamah (Shia doctrine)">Imam</a> of <a href="/wiki/Twelver" title="Twelver">Twelver</a> <a href="/wiki/Shia_Islam" title="Shia Islam">Shia Islam</a></small></span></th>
