<li id="cite_note-Yaan-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Yaan_7-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Yaan_7-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Yaan_7-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Richard, Yaan (1995). <i>Shi'ite Islam</i>. Oxford UK, Cambridge US: Blackwell.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMuhammad+al-Mahdi&amp;rft.aufirst=Yaan&amp;rft.aulast=Richard&amp;rft.au=Richard%2C+Yaan&amp;rft.btitle=Shi%27ite+Islam&amp;rft.date=1995&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.place=Oxford+UK%2C+Cambridge+US&amp;rft.pub=Blackwell&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
